                  <pb n="53"/>
                  <lb/>
               </p>
            </div>
            <div>
               <head>III.</head>
               <p>
                  <lb/>
                  <lb/>
THou, O God, who <normalised orig="givest" auto="true">give</normalised> grace to the <lb/>
