            <div>
               <head>I.</head>
               <p>
                  <lb/>
                  <lb/>
O My God, merciful and gracious, my <lb/>
soul groans under the loads of its <lb/>
own infirmity, when my spirit is willing, <lb/>
my <choice ana="illegible">
                     <sic><notvariant>fl</notvariant>*sh</sic>
                     <corr>flesh</corr>
                  </choice> is weak; my understanding foolish, <lb/>
